title: CoFiX v3.0 New Plan
body:
CoFiX will suspend liquidity mining and focus on real trade.

1. You can choose an asset to make a market

2. When the market making fund is withdrawn, it shall be withdrawn 

3. according to the equal proportion of funds in the capital pool
The transaction fee is 0.3%, 0.2% remains in the capital pool, and 0.1% enters the DAO
CoFiXCore

2021.10.11
